{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, the manuscript has placed a special emphasis on the practical applications of Large Language Models (LLMs) in the biopharmaceutical sector.",
    "Several successful case studies were detailed to highlight the strengths and limitations of these models.",
    "Each case study includes an in-depth analysis and critical evaluation of the respective models.",
    "It is especially crucial to diligently evaluate and address the associated concerns, risks, and potential pitfalls (Borji, 2023).",
    "It is believed that the integration of LLMs in drug discovery would greatly facilitate the acceleration of the drug discovery pipeline."
  ]
}